description:
She`s originally a GateKeeper from AEGIS Shanghai Branch. She had a mission to pursuit the Invader plane and somewhat landed in Japan. After the mission she chooses to live in Japan for a while.
When she was young, the government took her grandfather and brother away from her. Being left alone probably contributed to the awakening of her power (the Gate of Red Heat).
For her age, she`s smart. As young as 12, she`s already in 1st year high school. Not only is she intelligent, but she`s also a good cook. She cooks Chinese food in her past time. She loves anything produced by nature, like fruits, vegetables and animals.
name: Feng FeiLing
